metadata.name: ITS JUST A JOKE #1
metadata.description: ITS JUST A JOKE is the first-ever NFT joke card collection showcasing 52 unique digital cards. These cards come in three distinct tiers: Signature, Silver, and Gold, each offering cardholders an array of exclusive utilities and perks. Every card is a membership into the ‘Laugh Out Labs’ VIP Comedy Club and Private Access Streetwear brand. This drop includes jokes written by renowned comedians Norman Towns, Ksenia, Clayton Farris, and Mark Serrittella. These comedians have previously graced Emmy Award-winning shows on networks such as HBO, Comedy Central, ABC, truTV, BET, Adult Swim and MTV.
